              en: "1) Open a blank note (phone or computer, doesn't matter) and write the app name at the top. 2) Write five short sentences: \"What is it, who is it for, what pain does it solve, how is it different, what counts as success?\". 3) Open any AI and type: \"Critique this idea like an honest friend, not someone who loves me\". Paste the reply at the bottom of the note under \"Risks\". 4) Describe two <strong>example users</strong>: their age, job, how they use their phone, how they handle this today. 5) Keep the note somewhere safe (email it to yourself, Drive, Notion); losing it means starting over and that's exhausting."
