            release: { tr: "<strong>Firebase App Check</strong> aktif. Native modül entegrasyonu için <strong>development build / production build</strong> gerek (Expo Go'da çalışmaz; <code>@react-native-firebase/app-check</code> ile config plugin yapılandırılır). <strong>Play Integrity</strong> (Android) ve <strong>App Attest</strong> (iOS) ile uygulamanın gerçekliği doğrulanıyor. Sahte istemcilerin Firestore/Storage/AI Logic'e erişmesi engelleniyor. <span class='hint'>Authentication \"bu kullanıcı kim?\" sorusunu cevaplar; App Check \"bu istek hangi uygulamadan?\" sorusunu cevaplar.</span>", en: "<strong>Firebase App Check</strong> is enabled. Native module integration requires a <strong>development build / production build</strong> (does not work in Expo Go; configured via the <code>@react-native-firebase/app-check</code> config plugin). App authenticity is verified via <strong>Play Integrity</strong> (Android) and <strong>App Attest</strong> (iOS). Fake clients are blocked. <span class='hint'>Authentication answers \"who is the user?\"; App Check answers \"which app does this request come from?\"</span>" }
