              en: "1) Install a framework-appropriate \"notifications\" library (ask AI: \"how do I add local notifications in X framework\"). 2) Don't ask for notification permission on first launch; ask when the user tries to set a reminder. 3) Schedule a \"remind me tomorrow at 9\" notification and confirm it fires."
