              en: "1) Set up <strong>push infrastructure</strong> to send notifications from the server (follow item 6.5). 2) When the user taps a notification, open the app to the <strong>correct screen</strong> (not the blank home screen); e.g. tapping a new-message notification goes to the chat screen. 3) If a notification arrives while the app is open, show a small in-app banner; don't replicate the system notification."
