            en: "1) <strong>Regression test plan</strong>: a scenario set to run at every sprint end / every PR. 2) Test on <strong>3+ different devices</strong>: a new flagship, mid-range, old; small + large screens; iOS + Android. 3) Test every scenario in <strong>both dark and light themes</strong>. 4) Run <strong>5-10 external beta testers</strong>: TestFlight (iOS), Play Console Internal Testing (Android), staging URL (PWA). Prepare a feedback form. 5) Track crash + error rates on a dashboard (8.3); confirm below the release threshold. 6) A <strong>release go/no-go</strong> checklist: all critical tests PASS, no P1 bugs, store assets ready."
