            release: { tr: "Resimler <strong>lazy loaded</strong> ve doğru boyutta optimize edilmiş. ProMotion ekranlı (iPhone Pro / iPad Pro) cihazlarda <strong>120 fps</strong> alabilmek için <code>Info.plist</code>'e <strong><code>CADisableMinimumFrameDurationOnPhone</code> = <code>YES</code></strong> eklendi (bu anahtar yoksa Apple varsayılan olarak 60 fps'e kilitler). Profiling <strong>Xcode Instruments</strong> ile yapıldı: <strong>Time Profiler</strong> CPU sıcak yollar, <strong>Allocations / Leaks</strong> bellek, <strong>Hangs / Animation Hitches</strong> jank için. Kritik kod yollarında <strong><code>os_signpost</code></strong> (<code>OSSignposter</code>, <code>Logger</code> ile birlikte) kullanılarak Instruments'ta zaman aralıkları görselleştiriliyor. Memory leak yok; <code>weak</code> reference cycle'lar kontrol edildi (<code>[weak self]</code> closure'larda). IPA boyutu makul (App Thinning ile cihaza özel).", en: "Images are <strong>lazy-loaded</strong> and properly sized. To unlock <strong>120 fps</strong> on ProMotion devices (iPhone Pro / iPad Pro), <code>Info.plist</code> contains <strong><code>CADisableMinimumFrameDurationOnPhone</code> = <code>YES</code></strong> (without this key Apple caps animations at 60 fps by default). Profiling done with <strong>Xcode Instruments</strong>: <strong>Time Profiler</strong> for hot CPU paths, <strong>Allocations / Leaks</strong> for memory, <strong>Hangs / Animation Hitches</strong> for jank. Critical code paths use <strong><code>os_signpost</code></strong> (<code>OSSignposter</code> with <code>Logger</code>) so intervals are visualized in Instruments. No memory leaks; <code>weak</code> reference cycles are checked (<code>[weak self]</code> in closures). IPA size is reasonable (device-specific via App Thinning)." }
