            release: { tr: "Kritik akışlar için <strong>Playwright</strong> veya <strong>Cypress</strong> ile e2e testleri (mobil viewport dahil). Bileşen testleri <strong>@testing-library</strong> + Vitest/Jest ile. CI'da her PR'da koşuyor; başarısızsa merge bloklanıyor.", en: "End-to-end tests for critical flows with <strong>Playwright</strong> or <strong>Cypress</strong> (including mobile viewport). Component tests via <strong>@testing-library</strong> + Vitest/Jest. Runs on every PR in CI; failures block merge." }
